{"parentUuid":"a7bba1dc-ed95-449d-ad09-357ebdd04479","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"efc988f5-0888-498c-9d7e-1bbd61e6c876","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has provided detailed responses to each of the issues I identified in my review. They're asking me to verify their modifications are correct and to update the plan file with these revisions. Let me go through each one:\n\n1. **AD620 gain issue** - They accept the fix: G=100 + TL072/NE5532 second stage. This is correct.\n\n2. **Nyquist sampling** - They partially accept: changing to 4mm step (≤ λ/2). They want to keep scanning range same. This is reasonable.\n\n3. **Flyback diode** - They accept: replace 1N4007 with 1N5819. Correct fix.\n\n4. **3D print infill** - They accept: 100% infill for blocking rings, add aluminum foil tape. Good.\n\n5. **Axial manual positioning** - They accept: add steel ruler, document B-class uncertainty. Reasonable compromise.\n\n6. **COMSOL Sound Hard Boundary** - They correctly note this is not actually a problem, just needs a justification sentence in the report.\n\n7. They also added procurement list changes and report content changes.\n\nThis is all reasonable. Let me update the plan file to reflect these agreed changes. I should:\n- Update the original project document's parameters (step size, gain settings, diode selection)\n- Add the procurement list changes\n- Add the report content changes\n- Mark the review items as resolved\n\nSince we're in plan mode, I should edit the plan file to reflect these decisions.","signature":"efc988f5-0888-498c-9d7e-1bbd61e6c876"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3079,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":66432,"output_tokens":681,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"f94fb131-548e-44d4-9d51-6db263472e00","timestamp":"2026-05-29T12:31:21.662Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
{"parentUuid":"f94fb131-548e-44d4-9d51-6db263472e00","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"efc988f5-0888-498c-9d7e-1bbd61e6c876","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你的修正方案全部合理，我逐条确认一下：\n\n1. **AD620 G=100 + TL072 二级放大** — 正确，AD620 G=100 时 BW=120 kHz 足够，TL072（GBP=3 MHz）在 40 kHz 可提供 75 倍增益裕量，总增益 500-1000 倍没问题。Rg ≈ 500Ω 的计算也正确。\n\n2. **步长改为 4 mm** — ≤ λ/2=4.25 mm，严格满足 Nyquist，点数从 41 增到 51，时间增加约 20% 完全可以接受。\n\n3. **1N5819 统一替换** — 删掉 1N4007 和 1N4148，全部用 1N5819 既续流又检波，减少物料种类，方案更干净。\n\n4. **遮挡环 100% 填充 + 铝箔** — 低成本高效果。\n\n5. **z 轴钢直尺 + B 类不确定度文档化** — 性价比最高的方案。\n\n6. **Sound Hard Boundary 不是问题** — 只需报告里加一句阻抗比说明。\n\n现在把这些修正同步到计划文件中。"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3079,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":66432,"output_tokens":681,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"ba1e61ca-44fc-4415-9f2c-42cf5e08d25c","timestamp":"2026-05-29T12:31:27.680Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
