{"parentUuid":"c804fbc8-3c67-4646-9e5b-c2f101e1a3b0","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"3381c718-7e5f-4a72-a33e-07172a075cb1","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你的 6 项修正全部审查通过。核心要点：\n\n**P0 三项**（必须改，你都接受了）：\n- AD620 G=100 + TL072 → 信号链路带宽-增益平衡正确\n- 步长 4 mm → 满足 Nyquist，点数 41→51 可接受\n- 1N5819 统一替换 → 删掉 1N4007/1N4148，物料更干净\n\n**P1 两项**（你做了最优性价比选择）：\n- 遮挡环 100% 填充 + 铝箔，¥2 解决\n- z 轴钢尺 + B 类不确定度文档化，不增成本\n\n**P2 一项**（你正确识别为非问题）：\n- Sound Hard Boundary 近似误差 < 0.03%，写一句话即可\n\n**总成本 275→281 元**，仍在 300 元目标内。\n\n所有修正已写入计划文件第六节，包括变更后的采购清单和报告措辞。需要我做什么其他事吗？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":7753,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":72832,"output_tokens":383,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"3397a07f-fb86-4eda-b250-0b56a0e6bff4","timestamp":"2026-05-29T12:36:59.924Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
