{"type":"file-history-snapshot","messageId":"db8d5262-93f3-4c15-9641-dc7eb3f50e80","snapshot":{"messageId":"db8d5262-93f3-4c15-9641-dc7eb3f50e80","trackedFileBackups":{"D:\\钉钉\\学习工作文件\\物理实验创新竞赛\\超声菲涅尔波带片_实验仿真方案与审查报告.txt":{"backupFileName":"eddc95bc00476e1f@v3","version":3,"backupTime":"2026-05-30T00:45:42.597Z"},"D:\\钉钉\\学习工作文件\\物理实验创新竞赛\\超声菲涅尔波带片_完整项目执行方案_终版.txt":{"backupFileName":"47cac596a445be75@v2","version":2,"backupTime":"2026-05-31T03:23:20.320Z"},"C:\\Users\\Nijika\\.claude\\plans\\claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter.md":{"backupFileName":"55f0495606e8e9b1@v5","version":5,"backupTime":"2026-05-30T00:45:42.597Z"}},"timestamp":"2026-05-31T04:42:26.997Z"},"isSnapshotUpdate":false}
{"parentUuid":"db8d5262-93f3-4c15-9641-dc7eb3f50e80","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"21b2256b-7d9c-4a13-a68e-3f60b02d1dab","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how many limit switches they need. Let me think about the scanning platform:\n\nThe scanning platform has:\n- One T8 screw slide for radial scanning (r direction, automated by stepper motor)\n- The axial direction (z) is manual\n\nFor the radial scanning axis (the motorized one), you typically need:\n- 2 limit switches: one at each end of travel (r = -100mm and r = +100mm) to prevent the slider from crashing into the mechanical stops\n\nThe z-axis is manual so it doesn't need limit switches.\n\nSo the answer is **2 个**, one for each end of the radial scan range.","signature":"21b2256b-7d9c-4a13-a68e-3f60b02d1dab"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1149,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":149888,"output_tokens":559,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"3cd75515-2a93-42b2-a1ae-aaa30bc878a9","timestamp":"2026-05-31T04:42:33.911Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
{"parentUuid":"3cd75515-2a93-42b2-a1ae-aaa30bc878a9","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"21b2256b-7d9c-4a13-a68e-3f60b02d1dab","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**2 个**，装在径向滑台两端。\n\n---\n\n### 位置\n\n```\n  限位开关 1                         限位开关 2\n  (r = -100 mm)                     (r = +100 mm)\n       │                                  │\n       ▼                                  ▼\n  ┌────┴──────────────────────────────────┴────┐\n  │              T8 丝杆滑台                    │\n  └────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                    ▲\n                    │\n              滑块（探头）\n          来回扫，碰到开关就停\n```\n\n滑块移动到端点时碰到限位开关的金属弹片，信号传给 Arduino，固件立即停发 STEP 脉冲，防止滑块撞坏丝杆或电机丢步。\n\n---\n\n### 接线\n\n两个限位开关的接线一样，每个有 3 个脚（COM / NO / NC）：\n\n```\nArduino 内部上拉模式（最简单，不需要外接电阻）：\n\n    限位开关 COM ── Arduino GND\n    限位开关 NC  ── Arduino D8（限位1，-100mm端）\n    限位开关 NC  ── Arduino D9（限位2，+100mm端）\n    \n    固件里：pinMode(8, INPUT_PULLUP);\n           pinMode(9, INPUT_PULLUP);\n    \n    逻辑：正常时 NC 闭合→读到 LOW\n          碰到开关 NC 断开→读到 HIGH → 立即停止\n```\n\n用 NC（常闭）比 NO（常开）更安全——线断了也会触发\"碰到\"信号，电机不会跑飞。\n\n---\n\n### 汇总\n\n| 物品 | 数量 | 单价 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 机械限位开关 | 2 | ¥2-3 |\n| 杜邦线 母对母 | 4 根 | 已有 |\n\n搜 `限位开关 3D打印机 机械`，买跟 A4988 同店的那种 3 脚微动开关就行。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1149,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":149888,"output_tokens":559,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"5e6502bb-cf90-4e37-8cab-de876cd407e8","timestamp":"2026-05-31T04:42:42.776Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
