{"parentUuid":"0d16aa62-b529-407e-acf9-00de4164e117","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"8a09f65b-d3cc-44b4-97b3-b2fd684f4f36","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me write a comprehensive Python script that:\n\n1. Generates realistic simulated ultrasound field data using a simplified Fresnel diffraction model\n2. Creates pseudo-color heatmaps\n3. Performs 2D Gaussian sub-pixel fitting\n4. Extracts focal coordinates, FWHM, and gain\n5. Visualizes everything with proper plots\n6. Is modular so real data can be swapped in by just changing the data source\n\nThe physics model should be:\n- A simplified Fresnel-Kirchhoff diffraction calculation for the zone plate\n- Or even simpler: a 2D Gaussian + some diffraction rings + noise, which is a good approximation near the focus\n\nActually, let me do a proper simplified model. The acoustic field behind the zone plate at a point (r,z) can be approximated as the sum of contributions from each open ring:\n\nU(r,z) ∝ Σ_{m∈open} ∫_{ρ_{m-1}}^{ρ_m} ∫_0^{2π} exp(ikd)/d · ρ dθ dρ\n\nwhere d = sqrt(r² + ρ² - 2rρ cosθ + z²)\n\nThis is computationally heavy for a quick demo. Let me use a hybrid approach:\n- Use an analytical approximation for the on-axis field\n- Use a 2D Gaussian model for the focal region with realistic parameters\n- Add diffraction sidelobes\n- Add noise\n\nActually, let me think about what's most useful. The user wants to:\n1. Practice the data processing pipeline\n2. Test the Gaussian fitting\n3. Compare with COMSOL results\n\nThe best approach is a simplified but physically motivated model. Let me write it.\n\nFor the focal region, the field is approximately a 2D Gaussian plus some Bessel-function-like sidelobes. The key parameters:\n- FWHM_r ≈ λF/D = 8.5×120/219 ≈ 4.7mm (diffraction limit)\n- FWHM_z ≈ 2λ(F/D)² ≈ 2×8.5×(120/219)² ≈ 5.1mm (depth of focus)\n- But with only N=10 rings, it'll be wider\n- Realistic: FWHM_r ≈ 10-15mm, FWHM_z ≈ 25-35mm\n\nLet me use these parameters. I'll also add a `1/r` background decay, some sidelobe ripples, and noise.\n\nLet me write the complete script now.","signature":"8a09f65b-d3cc-44b4-97b3-b2fd684f4f36"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":974,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":194176,"output_tokens":7190,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"c9c3e804-fd98-4fd6-9f79-e0c29da50efd","timestamp":"2026-07-03T08:27:33.620Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
{"parentUuid":"c9c3e804-fd98-4fd6-9f79-e0c29da50efd","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"8a09f65b-d3cc-44b4-97b3-b2fd684f4f36","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_00_Cp5LN8mCOGJOIlOmyYBZ3888","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"D:\\钉钉\\学习工作文件\\物理实验创新竞赛\\声场仿真与亚像素分析.py","content":"# ===================================================================\n# 超声菲涅尔波带片 — 声场仿真 + 可视化 + 亚像素高斯拟合\n# ===================================================================\n# 【使用说明】\n#   本脚本不依赖任何硬件，在家就能跑。\n#   它分三部分：\n#     Part A：用物理模型生成仿真声场数据（模拟二维扫描结果）\n#     Part B：可视化（伪彩色热图 + 轴向/径向曲线）\n#     Part C：二维高斯亚像素拟合（提取焦点精确坐标 + FWHM）\n#\n#   当真实实验数据到手后，只需修改 Part A → 从 CSV 读取即可，\n#   Part B 和 Part C 完全不用改。\n#\n# 【运行环境】Python 3.x, numpy, scipy, matplotlib\n#   安装：pip install numpy scipy matplotlib\n# ===================================================================\n\nimport numpy as np\nfrom scipy.optimize import curve_fit\nfrom scipy.ndimage import maximum_filter\nimport matplotlib\nmatplotlib.use('TkAgg')  # 如果弹窗报错，改成 'Agg' 只保存图片不弹窗\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n# ===================================================================\n# Part A：生成仿真声场数据\n# ===================================================================\n\ndef generate_simulated_field(\n    z_range=(80, 160),    # mm\n    r_range=(-60, 60),    # mm\n    step_mm=4,            # mm\n    F_design=120,         # mm\n    wavelength=8.5,       # mm\n    D_lens=219.14,        # mm（透镜直径）\n    N_rings=10,\n    noise_level=0.02,     # 相对噪声水平\n    random_seed=42\n):\n    \"\"\"\n    用简化物理模型生成模拟的二维声场扫描数据。\n\n    模型组成：\n      1. 1/z 球面波衰减（基准背景）\n      2. 二维高斯峰（焦点主瓣，FWHM 由衍射极限估算）\n      3. 衍射旁瓣（焦点附近的微弱环形波纹）\n      4. 高斯随机噪声\n\n    返回：\n      z_vals, r_vals : 1D 坐标数组\n      field          : 2D 声压场, shape=(len(z_vals), len(r_vals))\n      params_true    : 真实焦点参数（用于验证拟合精度）\n    \"\"\"\n\n    # 坐标网格\n    z_vals = np.arange(z_range[0], z_range[1] + step_mm/2, step_mm)\n    r_vals = np.arange(r_range[0], r_range[1] + step_mm/2, step_mm)\n    R, Z = np.meshgrid(r_vals, z_vals)\n\n    # ---------- 1. 球面波衰减背景 ----------\n    # U ∝ 1/z（远场球面波，沿轴向）\n    background = 0.3 / (Z / 100)  # 归一化，让 z=100mm 处约 0.3\n\n    # ---------- 2. 焦点高斯峰 ----------\n    # 衍射极限焦斑估算：\n    #   FWHM_r_dl ≈ λF/D （瑞利判据，圆孔衍射）\n    #   FWHM_z_dl ≈ 2λ(F/D)²（焦深）\n    # 由于只有 N=10 个环（非完整透镜），实际焦斑比衍射极限宽\n    NA_eff = (D_lens/2) / F_design  # 有效数值孔径\n    fwhm_r_dl = wavelength / (2 * NA_eff)       # 衍射极限径向 FWHM\n    fwhm_z_dl = 2 * wavelength / (NA_eff ** 2)   # 衍射极限轴向 FWHM\n\n    # 实际有限环数展宽（N=10 约展宽 1.3-1.5 倍）\n    broadening = 1.0 + 2.0 / N_rings  # 约 1.2\n    fwhm_r = fwhm_r_dl * broadening\n    fwhm_z = fwhm_z_dl * broadening\n\n    sigma_r = fwhm_r / 2.355  # FWHM → σ\n    sigma_z = fwhm_z / 2.355\n\n    # 焦点位置：设计焦距 + 微小随机偏移（模拟加工误差）\n    rng = np.random.default_rng(random_seed)\n    r0_true = rng.uniform(-0.5, 0.5)     # 焦点 r 偏移 < 0.5mm\n    z0_true = F_design + rng.uniform(-3, 3)  # 焦点 z 偏移 < 3mm\n\n    # 焦点增益（相对背景）\n    A_true = 5.0  # 焦点处声压是背景的 ~5 倍，对应 Gain ≈ 14 dB\n\n    # 高斯峰\n    gaussian_peak = A_true * np.exp(\n        -((R - r0_true)**2) / (2 * sigma_r**2)\n        - ((Z - z0_true)**2) / (2 * sigma_z**2)\n    )\n\n    # ---------- 3. 衍射旁瓣 ----------\n    # 围绕焦点有几圈微弱的环形波纹（一阶贝塞尔函数的近似）\n    radial_dist = np.sqrt((R - r0_true)**2 + ((Z - z0_true) * 0.3)**2)\n    sidelobe_scale = radial_dist / (sigma_r * 2)\n    # 避免除零\n    sidelobe_scale = np.clip(sidelobe_scale, 0.1, None)\n    sidelobes = 0.15 * A_true * np.abs(np.sin(sidelobe_scale * np.pi)\n                                       / (sidelobe_scale + 0.01))\n    sidelobes *= np.exp(-radial_dist / (sigma_r * 6))  # 远处衰减\n\n    # ---------- 4. 组合 ----------\n    field = background + gaussian_peak + sidelobes\n\n    # 加噪声\n    noise = noise_level * rng.normal(0, 1, field.shape) * (background + 0.1)\n    field += noise\n\n    # 确保非负（声压幅值取绝对值后为非负）\n    field = np.abs(field)\n\n    # 真实参数记录\n    params_true = {\n        'r0': r0_true, 'z0': z0_true,\n        'sigma_r': sigma_r, 'sigma_z': sigma_z,\n        'A': A_true, 'B': np.mean(background),\n        'fwhm_r': fwhm_r, 'fwhm_z': fwhm_z,\n        'gain_db': 20 * np.log10(A_true / np.mean(background)),\n    }\n\n    return z_vals, r_vals, field, params_true\n\n\n# ===================================================================\n# Part B：可视化\n# ===================================================================\n\ndef plot_results(z_vals, r_vals, field, fit_result=None, params_true=None,\n                 save_prefix='simulated'):\n    \"\"\"\n    生成四张图：\n      1. 伪彩色声场热图\n      2. 轴向声压曲线 U(z) @ r=0\n      3. 焦平面径向曲线 U(r) @ z=z_max\n      4. 焦点邻域等高线 + 拟合结果\n    \"\"\"\n\n    R_grid, Z_grid = np.meshgrid(r_vals, z_vals)\n\n    # 找到粗峰值位置\n    idx_max = np.unravel_index(np.argmax(field), field.shape)\n    z_coarse = z_vals[idx_max[0]]\n    r_coarse = r_vals[idx_max[1]]\n\n    # 提取轴向和径向截面\n    # 轴向：r 最接近 0 的那一列\n    r_zero_idx = np.argmin(np.abs(r_vals))\n    axial_line = field[:, r_zero_idx]\n\n    # 径向：z 最接近粗峰值的那一行\n    z_peak_idx = np.argmin(np.abs(z_vals - z_coarse))\n    radial_line = field[z_peak_idx, :]\n\n    fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(14, 11))\n    fig.suptitle('Ultrasonic Fresnel Zone Plate — Simulated Acoustic Field',\n                 fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\n\n    # ---- 图 1：伪彩色热图 ----\n    ax1 = axes[0, 0]\n    im = ax1.pcolormesh(r_vals, z_vals, field, cmap='inferno',\n                        shading='auto')\n    ax1.axhline(y=120, color='cyan', linestyle='--', linewidth=1, alpha=0.7,\n                label='Design F=120mm')\n    if params_true:\n        ax1.plot(params_true['r0'], params_true['z0'], 'c*',\n                 markersize=18, markeredgewidth=1.5, markeredgecolor='white',\n                 label=f'True focus (r={params_true[\"r0\"]:.1f}, z={params_true[\"z0\"]:.1f})')\n    if fit_result:\n        ax1.plot(fit_result['r0'], fit_result['z0'], 'go',\n                 markersize=12, markerfacecolor='none', markeredgewidth=2,\n                 label=f'Fitted focus (r={fit_result[\"r0\"]:.1f}, z={fit_result[\"z0\"]:.1f})')\n    ax1.set_xlabel('r [mm]')\n    ax1.set_ylabel('z [mm]')\n    ax1.set_title('Acoustic Pressure Field (pseudo-color)')\n    ax1.legend(fontsize=8, loc='upper right')\n    ax1.set_ylim(z_vals[-1], z_vals[0])  # 翻转 z 轴（近→远）\n    plt.colorbar(im, ax=ax1, label='Pressure [a.u.]')\n\n    # ---- 图 2：轴向曲线 ----\n    ax2 = axes[0, 1]\n    ax2.plot(z_vals, axial_line, 'b-', linewidth=1.5, label='U(z) @ r=0')\n    ax2.axvline(x=120, color='cyan', linestyle='--', linewidth=1, alpha=0.7,\n                label='Design F=120mm')\n    if params_true:\n        ax2.axvline(x=params_true['z0'], color='yellow', linestyle=':',\n                    linewidth=1, alpha=0.8,\n                    label=f'True z0={params_true[\"z0\"]:.1f}')\n    if fit_result:\n        ax2.axvline(x=fit_result['z0'], color='green', linestyle='--',\n                    linewidth=1.5, label=f'Fitted z0={fit_result[\"z0\"]:.1f}')\n\n    # 标 FWHM_z\n    if fit_result:\n        half_max = (fit_result['A'] / 2) + fit_result['B']\n        ax2.axhline(y=half_max, color='red', linestyle=':', linewidth=0.8)\n        ax2.annotate(f'FWHM_z={fit_result[\"fwhm_z\"]:.1f}mm',\n                     xy=(fit_result['z0'], half_max),\n                     fontsize=9, color='red')\n\n    ax2.set_xlabel('z [mm]')\n    ax2.set_ylabel('Pressure [a.u.]')\n    ax2.set_title('Axial Pressure Profile')\n    ax2.legend(fontsize=8)\n    ax2.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n\n    # ---- 图 3：径向曲线 ----\n    ax3 = axes[1, 0]\n    ax3.plot(r_vals, radial_line, 'r-', linewidth=1.5,\n             label=f'U(r) @ z≈{z_coarse:.0f}mm')\n    ax3.axvline(x=0, color='gray', linestyle='--', linewidth=0.8, alpha=0.5)\n    if params_true:\n        ax3.axvline(x=params_true['r0'], color='yellow', linestyle=':',\n                    linewidth=1, alpha=0.8,\n                    label=f'True r0={params_true[\"r0\"]:.2f}')\n    if fit_result:\n        ax3.axvline(x=fit_result['r0'], color='green', linestyle='--',\n                    linewidth=1.5, label=f'Fitted r0={fit_result[\"r0\"]:.2f}')\n        half_max_r = (fit_result['A'] / 2) + fit_result['B']\n        ax3.axhline(y=half_max_r, color='red', linestyle=':', linewidth=0.8)\n        ax3.annotate(f'FWHM_r={fit_result[\"fwhm_r\"]:.1f}mm',\n                     xy=(0, half_max_r), fontsize=9, color='red')\n\n    ax3.set_xlabel('r [mm]')\n    ax3.set_ylabel('Pressure [a.u.]')\n    ax3.set_title('Focal Plane Radial Profile')\n    ax3.legend(fontsize=8)\n    ax3.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n\n    # ---- 图 4：焦点区域放大 + 拟合误差 ----\n    ax4 = axes[1, 1]\n    # 截取焦点附近区域\n    z_focal = fit_result['z0'] if fit_result else z_coarse\n    zoom_half = 25  # mm, 放大 ±25mm\n    z_mask = (z_vals >= z_focal - zoom_half) & (z_vals <= z_focal + zoom_half)\n    r_mask = (r_vals >= -zoom_half) & (r_vals <= zoom_half)\n    z_zoom = z_vals[z_mask]\n    r_zoom = r_vals[r_mask]\n    field_zoom = field[np.ix_(z_mask, r_mask)]\n\n    # 绘制轮廓填充\n    Rz, Zz = np.meshgrid(r_zoom, z_zoom)\n    levels = np.linspace(np.min(field_zoom), np.max(field_zoom), 12)\n    contour = ax4.contourf(Rz, Zz, field_zoom, levels=levels, cmap='inferno')\n    ax4.contour(Rz, Zz, field_zoom, levels=6, colors='white',\n                linewidths=0.5, alpha=0.5)\n\n    # 标注焦点\n    if fit_result:\n        ax4.plot(fit_result['r0'], fit_result['z0'], 'go',\n                 markersize=14, markerfacecolor='none', markeredgewidth=2.5)\n        # 画拟合误差椭圆（1σ 范围）\n        from matplotlib.patches import Ellipse\n        ellipse = Ellipse((fit_result['r0'], fit_result['z0']),\n                          width=2*fit_result['sigma_r'],\n                          height=2*fit_result['sigma_z'],\n                          edgecolor='lime', facecolor='none',\n                          linewidth=2, linestyle='--')\n        ax4.add_patch(ellipse)\n\n    if params_true:\n        ax4.plot(params_true['r0'], params_true['z0'], 'c+',\n                 markersize=16, markeredgewidth=2)\n\n    ax4.set_xlabel('r [mm]')\n    ax4.set_ylabel('z [mm]')\n    ax4.set_title('Focal Region Zoom (contours + 1σ ellipse)')\n    ax4.set_ylim(z_zoom[-1], z_zoom[0])\n    plt.colorbar(contour, ax=ax4, label='Pressure [a.u.]')\n\n    plt.tight_layout()\n    save_path = f'{save_prefix}_analysis.png'\n    plt.savefig(save_path, dpi=200, bbox_inches='tight')\n    print(f'[OK] 分析图已保存: {save_path}')\n    plt.show()\n\n\n# ===================================================================\n# Part C：亚像素高斯拟合\n# ===================================================================\n\ndef gaussian_2d(X, A, r0, z0, sigma_r, sigma_z, B):\n    \"\"\"二维高斯模型（用于拟合焦点邻域）\"\"\"\n    r, z = X\n    return A * np.exp(\n        -((r - r0)**2) / (2 * sigma_r**2)\n        - ((z - z0)**2) / (2 * sigma_z**2)\n    ) + B\n\n\ndef subpixel_fit(z_vals, r_vals, field, roi_half_size=5):\n    \"\"\"\n    亚像素焦点定位：对焦点邻域数据做二维高斯拟合。\n\n    步骤：\n      1. 找到网格上的粗最大值位置\n      2. 截取 ROI（通常 5×5 采样点，覆盖 ~20mm×20mm）\n      3. 用初值猜测做 Levenberg-Marquardt 非线性拟合\n      4. 从拟合参数提取焦点坐标、焦斑尺寸\n\n    参数：\n      z_vals, r_vals : 1D 坐标数组\n      field          : 2D 声压场\n      roi_half_size  : ROI 半径（采样点个数），5 → 11×11 网格\n\n    返回：\n      result : dict，含 r0, z0, sigma_r, sigma_z, A, B, fwhm_r, fwhm_z\n    \"\"\"\n\n    # 1. 找网格粗最大值\n    idx_max = np.unravel_index(np.argmax(field), field.shape)\n    z_idx_peak, r_idx_peak = idx_max\n\n    # 2. 截取 ROI（注意边界）\n    z_start = max(0, z_idx_peak - roi_half_size)\n    z_end = min(len(z_vals), z_idx_peak + roi_half_size + 1)\n    r_start = max(0, r_idx_peak - roi_half_size)\n    r_end = min(len(r_vals), r_idx_peak + roi_half_size + 1)\n\n    z_roi = z_vals[z_start:z_end]\n    r_roi = r_vals[r_start:r_end]\n    field_roi = field[z_start:z_end, r_start:r_end]\n\n    print(f'  ROI 大小: {field_roi.shape[0]}×{field_roi.shape[1]} 采样点')\n    print(f'  ROI 范围: z∈[{z_roi[0]:.0f},{z_roi[-1]:.0f}]mm, '\n          f'r∈[{r_roi[0]:.0f},{r_roi[-1]:.0f}]mm')\n\n    # 3. 初值猜测\n    U_max = np.max(field_roi)\n    U_bg = np.percentile(field_roi, 10)  # 第 10 百分位作为背景估计\n    r0_guess = r_vals[r_idx_peak]\n    z0_guess = z_vals[z_idx_peak]\n    # σ 初值 = 几个采样格子的宽度\n    sigma_r_guess = (r_vals[1] - r_vals[0]) * 2  # 约 8mm\n    sigma_z_guess = sigma_r_guess * 2.5           # 轴向通常比径向宽\n\n    p0 = [U_max, r0_guess, z0_guess, sigma_r_guess, sigma_z_guess, U_bg]\n\n    # 边界约束\n    bounds = (\n        [0,       r_roi[0],  z_roi[0],  0.5,      0.5,      0],      # 下限\n        [U_max*3, r_roi[-1], z_roi[-1], r_roi[-1], z_roi[-1], U_max] # 上限\n    )\n\n    # 4. 拟合\n    print(f'  初值猜测: r0={r0_guess:.1f}mm, z0={z0_guess:.1f}mm, '\n          f'sigma_r={sigma_r_guess:.1f}mm, sigma_z={sigma_z_guess:.1f}mm')\n\n    R_roi, Z_roi = np.meshgrid(r_roi, z_roi)\n    try:\n        popt, pcov = curve_fit(\n            gaussian_2d,\n            (R_roi.ravel(), Z_roi.ravel()),\n            field_roi.ravel(),\n            p0=p0,\n            bounds=bounds,\n            maxfev=10000,\n        )\n        # 参数误差（对角线元素平方根）\n        perr = np.sqrt(np.diag(pcov))\n    except RuntimeError as e:\n        print(f'  [警告] 拟合未收敛: {e}')\n        print(f'  使用初值作为近似结果')\n        popt = p0\n        perr = np.full(6, np.nan)\n\n    A_fit, r0_fit, z0_fit, sigma_r_fit, sigma_z_fit, B_fit = popt\n\n    result = {\n        'A': A_fit, 'B': B_fit,\n        'r0': r0_fit, 'z0': z0_fit,\n        'sigma_r': sigma_r_fit, 'sigma_z': sigma_z_fit,\n        'r0_err': perr[1], 'z0_err': perr[2],\n        'fwhm_r': 2.355 * sigma_r_fit,\n        'fwhm_z': 2.355 * sigma_z_fit,\n        'gain_db': 20 * np.log10(A_fit / B_fit) if B_fit > 0 else np.nan,\n    }\n\n    return result\n\n\ndef compare_methods(field, z_vals, r_vals, params_true, fit_result):\n    \"\"\"传统方法（网格最大值）vs 亚像素拟合（高斯拟合），并输出对比表\"\"\"\n    idx_max = np.unravel_index(np.argmax(field), field.shape)\n    coarse_z = z_vals[idx_max[0]]\n    coarse_r = r_vals[idx_max[1]]\n\n    step = z_vals[1] - z_vals[0]  # 步长\n\n    print('\\n' + '='*65)\n    print('焦点定位精度对比')\n    print('='*65)\n    print(f'{\"方法\":<20} {\"r0 [mm]\":>10} {\"z0 [mm]\":>10} {\"定位精度\":>12}')\n    print('-'*65)\n    print(f'{\"传统(网格max)\":<20} {coarse_r:>10.1f} {coarse_z:>10.1f} '\n          f'{f\"±{step/2:.1f}mm\":>12}')\n    if fit_result:\n        print(f'{\"亚像素(高斯拟合)\":<20} {fit_result[\"r0\"]:>10.2f} '\n              f'{fit_result[\"z0\"]:>10.2f} '\n              f'{f\"±0.5mm(估)\":>12}')\n\n    print('-'*65)\n    # 与真实值的偏差\n    if params_true and fit_result:\n        dr_grid = abs(coarse_r - params_true['r0'])\n        dz_grid = abs(coarse_z - params_true['z0'])\n        dr_fit = abs(fit_result['r0'] - params_true['r0'])\n        dz_fit = abs(fit_result['z0'] - params_true['z0'])\n        print(f'{\"网格法偏差\":<20} {dr_grid:>10.2f} {dz_grid:>10.2f}')\n        print(f'{\"拟合偏差\":<20} {dr_fit:>10.2f} {dz_fit:>10.2f}')\n        if dr_grid > 1e-6:\n            print(f'{\"提升倍数\":<20} {dr_grid/dr_fit:>10.1f}x '\n                  f'{dz_grid/dz_fit:>10.1f}x')\n    print('='*65)\n\n\n# ===================================================================\n# 主程序\n# ===================================================================\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    print('='*65)\n    print('超声菲涅尔波带片 — 声场仿真 + 亚像素定位')\n    print('='*65)\n\n    # ---- 1. 生成仿真数据 ----\n    print('\\n[Step 1] 生成仿真声场数据...')\n    z_vals, r_vals, field, params_true = generate_simulated_field(\n        z_range=(80, 160),\n        r_range=(-60, 60),\n        step_mm=4,\n        F_design=120,\n        wavelength=8.5,\n        noise_level=0.03,\n        random_seed=42\n    )\n    print(f'  扫描网格: z∈[{z_vals[0]:.0f},{z_vals[-1]:.0f}]mm, '\n          f'r∈[{r_vals[0]:.0f},{r_vals[-1]:.0f}]mm')\n    print(f'  步长: {z_vals[1]-z_vals[0]:.0f}mm,  '\n          f'共 {len(z_vals)}×{len(r_vals)} 个采样点')\n    print(f'  真实焦点: r0={params_true[\"r0\"]:.2f}mm, '\n          f'z0={params_true[\"z0\"]:.1f}mm')\n    print(f'  真实 FWHM: r={params_true[\"fwhm_r\"]:.1f}mm, '\n          f'z={params_true[\"fwhm_z\"]:.1f}mm')\n    print(f'  真实增益: {params_true[\"gain_db\"]:.1f} dB')\n\n    # ---- 2. 亚像素拟合 ----\n    print('\\n[Step 2] 亚像素高斯拟合...')\n    fit_result = subpixel_fit(z_vals, r_vals, field, roi_half_size=5)\n\n    print(f'\\n  拟合结果:')\n    print(f'    r0  = {fit_result[\"r0\"]:.3f} mm  (±{fit_result[\"r0_err\"]:.3f} mm)')\n    print(f'    z0  = {fit_result[\"z0\"]:.1f} mm  (±{fit_result[\"z0_err\"]:.1f} mm)')\n    print(f'    σ_r = {fit_result[\"sigma_r\"]:.2f} mm')\n    print(f'    σ_z = {fit_result[\"sigma_z\"]:.2f} mm')\n    print(f'    FWHM_r = {fit_result[\"fwhm_r\"]:.1f} mm')\n    print(f'    FWHM_z = {fit_result[\"fwhm_z\"]:.1f} mm')\n    print(f'    Gain   = {fit_result[\"gain_db\"]:.1f} dB')\n\n    # ---- 3. 对比 ----\n    print('\\n[Step 3] 定位精度对比...')\n    compare_methods(field, z_vals, r_vals, params_true, fit_result)\n\n    # ---- 4. 可视化 ----\n    print('\\n[Step 4] 生成可视化图表...')\n    plot_results(z_vals, r_vals, field,\n                 fit_result=fit_result,\n                 params_true=params_true,\n                 save_prefix='simulated')\n\n    # ---- 5. 导出 CSV（模拟真实实验的数据格式）----\n    print('\\n[Step 5] 导出仿真数据为 CSV（格式与真实实验一致）...')\n    with open('simulated_scan_data.csv', 'w') as f:\n        f.write('z_mm,r_mm,voltage_mv,temperature_c\\n')\n        for iz, z in enumerate(z_vals):\n            for ir, r in enumerate(r_vals):\n                # 电压缩放：假设 ADS1115 PGA=2, FSR=±2.048V\n                voltage = field[iz, ir] * 1000  # au → mV\n                f.write(f'{z:.1f},{r:.1f},{voltage:.3f},25.0\\n')\n    print(f'  已保存: simulated_scan_data.csv')\n    print(f'  格式: z_mm, r_mm, voltage_mv, temperature_c')\n\n    print('\\n' + '='*65)\n    print('完成！所有图表已生成，数据已导出。')\n    print('真实实验数据到手后，替换 Part A 为 pd.read_csv() 即可。')\n    print('='*65)\n\n\n# ===================================================================\n# 附录：真实数据替换模板\n# ===================================================================\n#\n# 当你有真实实验 CSV 后，删除上面的 generate_simulated_field() 调用，\n# 换成下面这段：\n#\n#   import pandas as pd\n#   df = pd.read_csv('real_scan.csv')  # 列名: z_mm, r_mm, voltage_mv, temperature_c\n#   z_vals = np.sort(df['z_mm'].unique())\n#   r_vals = np.sort(df['r_mm'].unique())\n#   field = df.pivot(index='z_mm', columns='r_mm', values='voltage_mv').values\n#   field = field / 1000  # mV → V（可选，不改也行）\n#\n#   # 下面的拟合和可视化代码完全不动，直接用。\n#\n# ===================================================================\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":974,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":194176,"output_tokens":7190,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"b6768b0c-f9bb-4b18-8c2c-f26ed3e329e5","timestamp":"2026-07-03T08:29:01.498Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
