{"parentUuid":"a1a4b313-dc3f-4215-903d-291ce7dd3b92","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"16e3a9f4-14bd-4810-8cee-a264393d99b2","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已更新为 5 人分工。调整逻辑：\n\n| 成员 | 原分工 | 现在 | 变化 |\n|------|--------|------|------|\n| 成员 1（组长）| 设计+仿真+算法+报告 | 设计+算法+报告+协调 | COMSOL 分出去了 |\n| 成员 2 | 硬件 | 硬件（不变）| — |\n| 成员 3 | 固件+软件 | 固件+软件（不变）| — |\n| 成员 4（新增）| — | COMSOL 仿真 | 从组长分出来的独立模块 |\n| 成员 5 | 3D 打印+机械+拍照 | 3D 打印+机械+拍照+文献+校对 | 加了不费脑但耗时的工作 |\n\n成员 5 的任务看起来不少（3D 建模/打印/组装/拍照/文献/排版），但实际上 3D 模型已有现成的、打印是学校的机器、照片随时拍——都是操作型的，不需要太深的物理或编程背景。表单里写得体面，实操上不会太累。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":158,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":244224,"output_tokens":291,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"c9b4d6fa-02f9-4c4e-adb0-091fff1db59f","timestamp":"2026-07-05T03:24:40.619Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
