{"parentUuid":"53a21325-f4cd-4d42-807f-635f244d2275","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"702a3ae2-830a-482b-9dc7-ec7dd955f0a9","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know if MATLAB can do the same acoustic simulation as COMSOL for their Fresnel zone plate project, and if I can help them with it.\n\nMATLAB can definitely do this - specifically using:\n1. The Partial Differential Equation Toolbox for FEM simulation\n2. Or more practically, numerical integration of the Fresnel-Kirchhoff diffraction integral\n\nThe second approach is actually more straightforward for this project and doesn't require expensive toolboxes. We can compute the acoustic field behind the zone plate using the Rayleigh-Sommerfeld or Fresnel-Kirchhoff diffraction integral.\n\nFor a 2D axisymmetric problem, the field at point (r,z) behind the zone plate is:\n\nU(r,z) = Σ_{m∈open} ∫_{ρ_{m-1}}^{ρ_m} ∫_0^{2π} (A/d) * exp(ikd) * ρ dθ dρ\n\nwhere d = sqrt(r² + ρ² - 2rρcosθ + z²)\n\nThis can be done in MATLAB with numerical integration. It's actually quite similar to what the Python script does with the simplified model.\n\nBut wait - the user's Python script already does a simplified version of this! The Python script uses a Gaussian approximation rather than the full diffraction integral. MATLAB could do the full numerical integration.\n\nHowever, there's a key issue: the user is already struggling with COMSOL, and MATLAB won't necessarily be easier. The MATLAB PDE Toolbox isn't as user-friendly for acoustics as COMSOL is. And doing the full diffraction integral in MATLAB requires writing the code from scratch.\n\nLet me think about what's realistic here:\n1. MATLAB can do this, yes\n2. But it requires either the PDE Toolbox (for FEM) or writing custom numerical integration code\n3. The custom code approach is actually simpler and more educational\n4. I can provide the MATLAB code\n\nActually, the most practical approach is:\n- Write a MATLAB script that computes the acoustic field using the Fresnel-Kirchhoff diffraction integral\n- This is essentially what I prototyped in Python but more physically accurate\n- No special toolboxes needed beyond basic MATLAB\n\nLet me write a MATLAB script for this. The key computation is:\n\nFor each observation point (r,z):\n  field = 0\n  for each open ring m:\n    for theta from 0 to 2π:\n      for rho from ρ_{m-1} to ρ_m:\n        d = sqrt(r² + ρ² - 2rρcosθ + z²)\n        field += exp(1i*k*d) / d * ρ * dρ * dθ\n\nThis is computationally heavy for a full 2D grid. Let me think about optimizations...\n\nFor 2D axisymmetric, we can use the fact that the integrand over θ has a closed form involving Bessel functions:\n\n∫_0^{2π} exp(ik sqrt(r² + ρ² - 2rρcosθ + z²)) / sqrt(r² + ρ² - 2rρcosθ + z²) dθ\n\nThis doesn't have a simple closed form, unfortunately. But we can use numerical integration with fewer points.\n\nActually, a more practical approach for MATLAB:\n1. Use the Fresnel approximation for the diffraction integral (valid near the optical axis)\n2. Or do the full integral with coarse sampling for quick results\n\nLet me write a MATLAB script that:\n1. Computes the acoustic field using numerical integration\n2. Generates heatmaps\n3. Performs Gaussian fitting for sub-pixel localization\n4. Works without any toolboxes (just base MATLAB)\n\nActually, let me be practical. The key insight is:\n\nFor the ON-AXIS field (r=0), the integral simplifies significantly:\nd = sqrt(ρ² + z²)\nThe θ integral gives 2π\nU(0,z) = 2π * Σ_{m∈open} ∫_{ρ_{m-1}}^{ρ_m} exp(ik sqrt(ρ²+z²)) / sqrt(ρ²+z²) * ρ dρ\n\nThis can be computed very quickly and gives the axial profile.\n\nFor the full 2D field, we need the off-axis computation which is more expensive but still doable with vectorization.\n\nLet me write a complete MATLAB script. I'll try to make it efficient using vectorized operations where possible.\n\nActually, the simplest approach that will work and give good results:\n\n1. For each (r,z) point, compute the contribution from each open ring\n2. Each ring contribution: integrate over ρ and θ\n3. Use `integral2` for the double integral, or manual summation\n\nFor speed, I can:\n- Pre-compute the integrand on a grid\n- Use symmetry (the field is symmetric in r → -r)\n- Use a coarser grid first, then refine around the focus\n\nLet me write the script. I'll make it complete with visualization and Gaussian fitting.\n\nActually, thinking about this more - MATLAB's `integral2` might be slow for thousands of points. Let me use a simpler approach: manual Riemann sum over ρ and θ with moderate resolution, vectorized over the observation grid.\n\nFor the 2D field computation, the most efficient approach in MATLAB:\n- Create a grid of observation points (r,z)\n- For each ring, do a double loop over ρ and θ\n- Accumulate contributions\n\nThis should take a few minutes for a reasonable grid.\n\nLet me write the complete script now.","signature":"702a3ae2-830a-482b-9dc7-ec7dd955f0a9"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1389,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":246400,"output_tokens":5919,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"7fb3a78d-ab0b-4f92-9bb9-28cb2e5cc26b","timestamp":"2026-07-05T04:05:08.506Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
{"parentUuid":"7fb3a78d-ab0b-4f92-9bb9-28cb2e5cc26b","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"702a3ae2-830a-482b-9dc7-ec7dd955f0a9","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MATLAB 完全可以做，而且不需要 PDE Toolbox——用基尔霍夫衍射积分直接数值计算就行。本质上就是用 MATLAB 把声波经过每个开放环带后的叠加算出来，比 COMSOL 更透明、更容易理解每一步在算什么。\n\n我帮你把完整脚本写出来。"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1389,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":246400,"output_tokens":5919,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"36afd984-3d4c-4a0b-ad87-26ecde052305","timestamp":"2026-07-05T04:05:09.709Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
{"parentUuid":"36afd984-3d4c-4a0b-ad87-26ecde052305","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"702a3ae2-830a-482b-9dc7-ec7dd955f0a9","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_00_HLswJ3R6b0m4BeAptau63007","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"D:\\钉钉\\学习工作文件\\物理实验创新竞赛\\fresnel_sim.m","content":"% ===================================================================\n% 超声菲涅尔波带片 — MATLAB 声场仿真 + 亚像素高斯拟合\n% ===================================================================\n% 【环境要求】MATLAB R2020a 及以上，无需任何额外 Toolbox\n% 【运行方式】将本文件放到工作目录，在命令窗口输入 fresnel_sim\n% 【计算时间】默认网格约 2-5 分钟（取决于 CPU）\n% ===================================================================\n\nfunction fresnel_sim()\n    close all; clc;\n    tic;\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 1. 物理参数\n    % =================================================================\n    f0      = 40000;        % 超声频率 [Hz]\n    c_air   = 340;          % 空气中声速 [m/s]\n    lambda  = c_air / f0;   % 波长 [m]\n    k       = 2 * pi / lambda;  % 波数 [rad/m]\n    F_design = 120e-3;      % 设计焦距 [m]\n\n    fprintf('超声菲涅尔波带片声场仿真\\n');\n    fprintf('========================\\n');\n    fprintf('频率: %.0f kHz\\n', f0/1000);\n    fprintf('波长: %.1f mm\\n', lambda*1000);\n    fprintf('设计焦距: %.0f mm\\n', F_design*1000);\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 2. 波带片环带参数 (Soret 型, N=10)\n    % =================================================================\n    N_rings = 10;\n    % 环带外半径 [m]\n    radii_mm = zeros(1, N_rings);\n    for m = 1:N_rings\n        radii_mm(m) = sqrt(m * lambda/2 * (2*F_design + m*lambda/2)) * 1000;\n    end\n\n    fprintf('\\n环带参数 (Soret 型, N=%d):\\n', N_rings);\n    fprintf('环号  外半径[mm]  状态\\n');\n    for m = 1:N_rings\n        status = '遮挡';\n        if mod(m, 2) == 1\n            status = '开放';\n        end\n        fprintf(' %2d    %7.2f     %s\\n', m, radii_mm(m), status);\n    end\n\n    % 开放环的索引（奇数环: 1,3,5,7,9）\n    open_rings = 1:2:N_rings;\n\n    % 环带内半径 [m]（第 m 环的内半径 = 第 m-1 环的外半径）\n    r_inner = [0, radii_mm(1:end-1)] / 1000;  % [m]\n    r_outer = radii_mm / 1000;                 % [m]\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 3. 观测网格\n    % =================================================================\n    % 为加快计算，先用较粗的网格，后续可在焦点附近加密\n    do_quick = true;  % true=快速预览(约30秒), false=完整计算(约5分钟)\n\n    if do_quick\n        % 快速预览网格\n        z_obs_mm = 60:10:180;    % 轴向 [mm]\n        r_obs_mm = 0:5:50;       % 径向 [mm]（只需正半轴，轴对称）\n        n_rho    = 8;            % 环带径向积分点\n        n_theta  = 36;           % 环带角度积分点\n    else\n        % 完整网格\n        z_obs_mm = 60:4:180;     % 轴向 [mm]\n        r_obs_mm = 0:2:60;       % 径向 [mm]\n        n_rho    = 16;           % 环带径向积分点\n        n_theta  = 72;           % 环带角度积分点\n    end\n\n    nz = length(z_obs_mm);\n    nr = length(r_obs_mm);\n    fprintf('\\n网格: %d x %d = %d 个观测点\\n', nz, nr, nz*nr);\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 4. 声场计算 — 基尔霍夫衍射积分\n    % =================================================================\n    % 对每个观测点 (r,z)，计算所有开放环带的贡献：\n    %   U(r,z) = Σ_{m in open} ∫∫ exp(ikd)/d * dS\n    %   其中 d = sqrt(r² + ρ² - 2rρcosθ + z²)\n    %\n    % 轴向点 (r=0) 有解析简化：d = sqrt(ρ² + z²)，可大幅加速\n\n    fprintf('\\n计算声场...\\n');\n\n    % 预分配\n    field = zeros(nz, nr);\n\n    % 积分点\n    theta_vals = linspace(0, 2*pi, n_theta+1);\n    theta_vals = theta_vals(1:end-1);  % 去掉重复的 2π\n    dtheta = 2*pi / n_theta;\n\n    for iz = 1:nz\n        z_obs = z_obs_mm(iz) / 1000;  % [m]\n        for ir = 1:nr\n            r_obs = r_obs_mm(ir) / 1000;  % [m]\n\n            U = 0;  % 复声压累加\n\n            % 判断是否在轴线上（可简化计算）\n            on_axis = (r_obs < 1e-9);\n\n            for m = open_rings\n                r_in = r_inner(m);\n                r_out = r_outer(m);\n\n                % 径向积分点\n                rho_vals = linspace(r_in, r_out, n_rho);\n                drho = (r_out - r_in) / (n_rho - 1);\n\n                for rho = rho_vals\n                    if on_axis\n                        % 轴线上：d = sqrt(rho² + z²)，θ 积分 = 2π\n                        d = sqrt(rho^2 + z_obs^2);\n                        U = U + exp(1i * k * d) / d * rho * drho * 2*pi;\n                    else\n                        % 离轴：需对 θ 积分\n                        for theta = theta_vals\n                            % 源点坐标\n                            x_s = rho * cos(theta);\n                            y_s = rho * sin(theta);\n                            % 距离\n                            d = sqrt((r_obs - x_s)^2 + y_s^2 + z_obs^2);\n                            U = U + exp(1i * k * d) / d * rho * drho * dtheta;\n                        end\n                    end\n                end\n            end\n\n            field(iz, ir) = abs(U);  % 取声压幅值\n        end\n\n        % 进度显示\n        if mod(iz, 5) == 0 || iz == nz\n            fprintf('  进度: %d/%d (%.0f%%)\\n', iz, nz, iz/nz*100);\n        end\n    end\n\n    % 转为 dB 尺度\n    field_dB = 20 * log10(field / max(field(:)));\n\n    fprintf('计算完成，耗时 %.1f 秒\\n', toc);\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 5. 无波带片对照（纯球面波衰减）\n    % =================================================================\n    % 无波带片时，声波直接从发射探头扩散到观测点\n    % U_no ~ 1/r（球面波远场近似），归一化到相同尺度\n    field_no = zeros(nz, nr);\n    for iz = 1:nz\n        z_obs = z_obs_mm(iz) / 1000;\n        for ir = 1:nr\n            r_obs = r_obs_mm(ir) / 1000;\n            d = sqrt(r_obs^2 + (z_obs + 0.300)^2);  % 发射探头在 z=-300mm\n            field_no(iz, ir) = 1 / d;\n        end\n    end\n    field_no_dB = 20 * log10(field_no / max(field_no(:)));\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 6. 找到峰值（粗定位）\n    % =================================================================\n    [~, idx_max] = max(field(:));\n    [iz_peak, ir_peak] = ind2sub(size(field), idx_max);\n    z_coarse = z_obs_mm(iz_peak);\n    r_coarse = r_obs_mm(ir_peak);\n\n    fprintf('\\n网格粗定位:\\n');\n    fprintf('  峰值位置: z = %.0f mm, r = %.0f mm\\n', z_coarse, r_coarse);\n    fprintf('  设计焦距偏差: %.1f mm\\n', z_coarse - 120);\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 7. 亚像素高斯拟合\n    % =================================================================\n    fprintf('\\n亚像素二维高斯拟合...\\n');\n\n    % 截取峰值附近 ROI\n    roi_half = 5;  % 网格点数\n    iz1 = max(1, iz_peak - roi_half);\n    iz2 = min(nz, iz_peak + roi_half);\n    ir1 = max(1, ir_peak - roi_half);\n    ir2 = min(nr, ir_peak + roi_half);\n\n    z_roi = z_obs_mm(iz1:iz2);\n    r_roi = r_obs_mm(ir1:ir2);\n    field_roi = field(iz1:iz2, ir1:ir2);\n\n    [Zg, Rg] = meshgrid(z_roi, r_roi);\n    Zg = Zg'; Rg = Rg';  % 转置使与 field_roi 对齐\n\n    % 初值猜测\n    A0  = max(field_roi(:)) - min(field_roi(:));\n    r00 = r_coarse;\n    z00 = z_coarse;\n    sr0 = 5;    % sigma_r 初值 [mm]\n    sz0 = 15;   % sigma_z 初值 [mm]\n    B0  = min(field_roi(:));\n\n    p0 = [A0, r00, z00, sr0, sz0, B0];\n\n    % 高斯模型\n    gauss2d = @(p, Z, R) p(1) * exp(-((R-p(2)).^2)/(2*p(4)^2) ...\n                                    - ((Z-p(3)).^2)/(2*p(5)^2)) + p(6);\n\n    % 拟合\n    Z_flat = Zg(:); R_flat = Rg(:); F_flat = field_roi(:);\n    try\n        p_fit = lsqcurvefit(gauss2d, p0, [Z_flat, R_flat], F_flat, ...\n                            [-inf, r_roi(1), z_roi(1), 0.5, 0.5, 0], ...\n                            [ inf, r_roi(end), z_roi(end), ...\n                              r_roi(end), z_roi(end), inf]);\n\n        A_fit  = p_fit(1);\n        r0_fit = p_fit(2);\n        z0_fit = p_fit(3);\n        sr_fit = p_fit(4);\n        sz_fit = p_fit(5);\n        B_fit  = p_fit(6);\n\n        FWHM_r = 2.355 * sr_fit;\n        FWHM_z = 2.355 * sz_fit;\n\n        fprintf('  亚像素拟合结果:\\n');\n        fprintf('    r0    = %.2f mm\\n', r0_fit);\n        fprintf('    z0    = %.1f mm\\n', z0_fit);\n        fprintf('    FWHM_r = %.1f mm\\n', FWHM_r);\n        fprintf('    FWHM_z = %.1f mm\\n', FWHM_z);\n        fprintf('    焦距偏差 = %.1f mm (%.1f%%)\\n', ...\n                abs(z0_fit - 120), abs(z0_fit - 120)/120*100);\n\n        % 传统 vs 亚像素对比\n        fprintf('\\n  精度对比:\\n');\n        fprintf('    传统(网格max): z=%.0f mm, r=%.0f mm, 精度=±%.1f mm\\n', ...\n                z_coarse, r_coarse, (z_obs_mm(2)-z_obs_mm(1))/2);\n        fprintf('    亚像素(拟合):  z=%.1f mm, r=%.2f mm\\n', z0_fit, r0_fit);\n        fprintf('    提升: z方向 %.1f 倍\\n', ...\n                abs(z_coarse-z0_fit)/(abs(z_coarse-z0_fit)+0.01));\n\n    catch\n        fprintf('  拟合未收敛，使用网格最大值\\n');\n        r0_fit = r_coarse;\n        z0_fit = z_coarse;\n        FWHM_r = NaN;\n        FWHM_z = NaN;\n    end\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 8. 可视化（四合一）\n    % =================================================================\n    fprintf('\\n生成图表...\\n');\n\n    figure('Position', [100, 100, 1400, 1000], 'Name', ...\n           '超声菲涅尔波带片声场仿真');\n\n    % --- (a) 声场热图 ---\n    subplot(2,2,1);\n    imagesc(r_obs_mm, z_obs_mm, field_dB);\n    colormap(gca, jet);\n    colorbar;\n    set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal');\n    hold on;\n    plot(r0_fit, z0_fit, 'go', 'MarkerSize', 12, ...\n         'MarkerFaceColor', 'none', 'LineWidth', 2);\n    yline(120, 'c--', 'LineWidth', 1.5);\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('z [mm]');\n    title(sprintf('(a) 声压分布 [dB]\\n焦点: r=%.1f, z=%.1f mm', r0_fit, z0_fit));\n    caxis([-20, 0]);\n\n    % --- (b) 轴向声压曲线 ---\n    subplot(2,2,2);\n    axial = field(:, 1);  % r=0 列\n    plot(z_obs_mm, axial / max(axial), 'b-', 'LineWidth', 2);\n    hold on;\n    xline(z0_fit, 'g--', 'LineWidth', 1.5);\n    xline(120, 'c--', 'LineWidth', 1);\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('z [mm]'); ylabel('归一化声压');\n    title('(b) 轴向声压曲线 U(z) | r=0');\n    legend('U(z)', sprintf('z_0=%.1fmm', z0_fit), 'F=120mm', ...\n           'Location', 'best');\n    grid on;\n\n    % --- (c) 焦平面径向曲线 ---\n    subplot(2,2,3);\n    radial = field(iz_peak, :);\n    plot(r_obs_mm, radial / max(radial), 'r-', 'LineWidth', 2);\n    hold on;\n    xline(r0_fit, 'g--', 'LineWidth', 1.5);\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('归一化声压');\n    title(sprintf('(c) 焦平面径向曲线 U(r) | z=%.0fmm', z_coarse));\n    grid on;\n\n    % --- (d) 焦点区域等高线 ---\n    subplot(2,2,4);\n    zm = (z_obs_mm >= z0_fit - 25) & (z_obs_mm <= z0_fit + 25);\n    rm = (r_obs_mm >= r0_fit - 25) & (r_obs_mm <= r0_fit + 25);\n    contourf(r_obs_mm(rm), z_obs_mm(zm), field(zm, rm), 20);\n    colormap(gca, jet);\n    colorbar;\n    set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal');\n    hold on;\n    plot(r0_fit, z0_fit, 'go', 'MarkerSize', 12, ...\n         'MarkerFaceColor', 'none', 'LineWidth', 2.5);\n    % 画 1σ 椭圆\n    th = linspace(0, 2*pi, 100);\n    plot(r0_fit + sr_fit*cos(th), z0_fit + sz_fit*sin(th), ...\n         'g--', 'LineWidth', 1.5);\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('z [mm]');\n    title(sprintf(['(d) 焦点区域 (1σ椭圆)\\n', ...\n                   'FWHM_r=%.1f, FWHM_z=%.1f mm'], FWHM_r, FWHM_z));\n\n    sgtitle('超声菲涅尔波带片 — MATLAB 基尔霍夫衍射积分仿真', ...\n            'FontSize', 14, 'FontWeight', 'bold');\n\n    saveas(gcf, 'matlab_fresnel_results.png');\n    fprintf('图表已保存: matlab_fresnel_results.png\\n');\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 9. 有无波带片对比图\n    % =================================================================\n    figure('Position', [150, 150, 1000, 400], 'Name', '聚焦效果对比');\n\n    subplot(1,2,1);\n    imagesc(r_obs_mm, z_obs_mm, field_dB);\n    colormap(gca, jet); colorbar;\n    set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal');\n    hold on;\n    plot(r0_fit, z0_fit, 'go', 'MarkerSize', 12, ...\n         'MarkerFaceColor', 'none', 'LineWidth', 2);\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('z [mm]');\n    title('(a) 有波带片 (N=10, F=120mm)');\n    caxis([-20, 0]);\n\n    subplot(1,2,2);\n    imagesc(r_obs_mm, z_obs_mm, field_no_dB);\n    colormap(gca, jet); colorbar;\n    set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal');\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('z [mm]');\n    title('(b) 无波带片 (纯球面波衰减)');\n    caxis([-20, 0]);\n\n    sgtitle('菲涅尔波带片聚焦效应验证', 'FontSize', 14, 'FontWeight', 'bold');\n    saveas(gcf, 'matlab_fresnel_comparison.png');\n    fprintf('对比图已保存: matlab_fresnel_comparison.png\\n');\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 10. 导出数据\n    % =================================================================\n    fprintf('\\n导出数据...\\n');\n    % 保存完整数据\n    save('matlab_fresnel_data.mat', ...\n         'z_obs_mm', 'r_obs_mm', 'field', 'field_dB', ...\n         'r0_fit', 'z0_fit', 'FWHM_r', 'FWHM_z', 'lambda', 'F_design');\n    fprintf('数据已保存: matlab_fresnel_data.mat\\n');\n\n    % 导出 CSV（与 Python 格式一致）\n    fid = fopen('matlab_scan_data.csv', 'w');\n    fprintf(fid, 'z_mm,r_mm,pressure_au,dB\\n');\n    for iz = 1:nz\n        for ir = 1:nr\n            fprintf(fid, '%.1f,%.1f,%.6f,%.2f\\n', ...\n                    z_obs_mm(iz), r_obs_mm(ir), field(iz,ir), field_dB(iz,ir));\n        end\n    end\n    fclose(fid);\n    fprintf('CSV已保存: matlab_scan_data.csv\\n');\n\n    fprintf('\\n============ 完成 ============\\n');\n    fprintf('总耗时: %.1f 秒\\n', toc);\nend\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1389,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":246400,"output_tokens":5919,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"e5f18a1b-6be6-47c3-a71b-0f9c4e4e7f2c","timestamp":"2026-07-05T04:05:58.593Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
