{"parentUuid":"e075c65e-b705-496a-a771-9c5f84bc3478","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"4ec8d8d2-661a-498d-82ab-e955451175d7","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what this file is for and doesn't understand the filename. Let me explain:\n\n1. `fresnel_sim.m` - This is a MATLAB script file. `.m` is the MATLAB file extension, and `fresnel_sim` is short for \"Fresnel simulation\". \n\n2. What it does: It's a complete MATLAB replacement for the COMSOL simulation. It computes the acoustic field behind the Fresnel zone plate using the Kirchhoff diffraction integral (numerical integration), finds the focus via sub-pixel Gaussian fitting, and generates the same 4-panel visualization + comparison charts.\n\nThe user rejected the write, so they want me to explain first before writing. Let me explain clearly what it is and what the filename means.","signature":"4ec8d8d2-661a-498d-82ab-e955451175d7"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":82,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":253696,"output_tokens":490,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"d02a3cc2-7193-43a3-ac4c-8fe01557cef1","timestamp":"2026-07-05T04:08:53.821Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
{"parentUuid":"d02a3cc2-7193-43a3-ac4c-8fe01557cef1","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"4ec8d8d2-661a-498d-82ab-e955451175d7","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个是 **MATLAB 声场仿真脚本**。文件名拆开：\n\n- `fresnel` = 菲涅尔\n- `sim` = simulation（仿真）\n- `.m` = MATLAB 脚本文件的后缀（就像 Python 的 `.py`）\n\n**它是干什么的**：把你们 COMSOL 队友要做的事，用 MATLAB 代码重写了一遍。运行后自动完成：\n\n1. 计算 40kHz 超声波通过波带片后的声压分布（基尔霍夫衍射积分）\n2. 找焦点（亚像素高斯拟合）\n3. 生成四张图（热图 + 轴向曲线 + 径向曲线 + 焦点放大）\n4. 导出 CSV 数据\n\n**和 Python 脚本的区别**：\n\n| | Python 脚本 | MATLAB 脚本 |\n|------|-----------|-----------|\n| 声场怎么算 | 用高斯峰+旁瓣近似 | 用基尔霍夫衍射积分正经算 |\n| 物理准确性 | 近似模型，够用 | 更接近真实物理 |\n| 计算时间 | 秒级 | 几分钟 |\n| 用途 | 练手、验证流程 | 正式仿真结果，可替代 COMSOL |\n\n也就是说 MATLAB 这份跑出来的结果，可以直接作为竞赛报告里的\"理论仿真\"部分，跟 COMSOL 的结果地位相同。两个独立方法算出来焦点都在 120mm 附近的话，就是交叉验证，更好。\n\n---\n\n**用不用我把它写出来？文件名可以改成你喜欢的，比如 `波带片声场仿真.m`。**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":82,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":253696,"output_tokens":490,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"04574390-b6cc-462e-bdb6-cf3832302f86","timestamp":"2026-07-05T04:08:58.968Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
