{"parentUuid":"41bf3aad-1ba1-413f-b557-0e1aabb6dda5","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"bb72ae7d-ec82-40d3-a6a7-1bfb05e9faa3","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking two questions:\n\n1. Can the entire simulation be done with MATLAB script code?\n2. After they install MATLAB, can they just hand it over to me to do everything?\n\nThe answer to both is YES. MATLAB can be controlled entirely through scripts, and Claude Code can run MATLAB via Bash commands (just like running Python scripts). The workflow would be:\n\n1. User installs MATLAB\n2. I write the complete `.m` script\n3. I run it via `matlab -batch \"fresnel_sim\"` in Bash\n4. I check the output, tweak parameters, re-run\n5. Generate all figures and data\n\nThis is much simpler than COMSOL via MCP because:\n- MATLAB is just running a script file, not interacting with a GUI\n- I can directly edit the `.m` file and re-run\n- No MCP interface needed - just Bash + file editing\n\nLet me confirm this and write the complete script.","signature":"bb72ae7d-ec82-40d3-a6a7-1bfb05e9faa3"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":93,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":254208,"output_tokens":5127,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"742c20db-02df-45ba-9913-c7a0d93596bc","timestamp":"2026-07-05T04:27:20.748Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
{"parentUuid":"742c20db-02df-45ba-9913-c7a0d93596bc","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"bb72ae7d-ec82-40d3-a6a7-1bfb05e9faa3","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**对，完全正确。**\n\nMATLAB 和 COMSOL 最大的区别就是：COMSOL 需要通过 MCP 接口一步步点 GUI，MATLAB 全程就是一个脚本文件，跟 Python 一模一样。\n\n你装好 MATLAB 之后，我做的事情就是：\n\n```\n1. 写 fresnel_sim.m 脚本     ← 我写，跟你写 Python 脚本一样\n2. 终端跑 matlab -batch \"fresnel_sim\"  ← 命令行一句就跑完了\n3. 看结果图，调参数，再跑    ← 改几行代码，重复步骤 2\n4. 所有图和数据自动保存到文件夹\n```\n\n不需要 MCP、不需要 GUI、不需要那个队友摸索 COMSOL 界面。\n\n---\n\n把脚本写出来吧？"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":93,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":254208,"output_tokens":5127,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"8060007a-a533-4c30-8faf-8169f06d2d61","timestamp":"2026-07-05T04:27:23.839Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
{"parentUuid":"8060007a-a533-4c30-8faf-8169f06d2d61","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"bb72ae7d-ec82-40d3-a6a7-1bfb05e9faa3","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_00_GNiRXKQEnfawXq6CLctl5708","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"D:\\钉钉\\学习工作文件\\物理实验创新竞赛\\fresnel_sim.m","content":"% ===================================================================\n% 超声菲涅尔波带片 — MATLAB 声场仿真 + 亚像素高斯拟合\n% ===================================================================\n% 【环境要求】MATLAB R2020a 及以上，无需任何额外 Toolbox\n% 【运行方式】在 MATLAB 命令窗口输入: fresnel_sim\n% 【计算时间】快速模式 ~30 秒，完整模式 ~3-5 分钟\n% ===================================================================\n\nfunction fresnel_sim()\n    close all; clc;\n    t_start = tic;\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 1. 物理参数\n    % =================================================================\n    f0      = 40000;         % 超声频率 [Hz]\n    c_air   = 340;           % 空气中声速 [m/s]\n    lambda  = c_air / f0;    % 波长 [m]\n    k       = 2 * pi / lambda;\n    F_design = 120e-3;       % 设计焦距 [m]\n\n    fprintf('========================================\\n');\n    fprintf('  超声菲涅尔波带片声场仿真 (MATLAB)\\n');\n    fprintf('========================================\\n');\n    fprintf('  频率:      %.0f kHz\\n', f0/1000);\n    fprintf('  波长:      %.1f mm\\n', lambda*1000);\n    fprintf('  设计焦距:  %.0f mm\\n', F_design*1000);\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 2. 波带片环带参数 (Soret 型, N=10)\n    % =================================================================\n    N_rings = 10;\n    radii_mm = zeros(1, N_rings);\n    for m = 1:N_rings\n        radii_mm(m) = sqrt(m * lambda/2 * (2*F_design + m*lambda/2)) * 1000;\n    end\n\n    fprintf('\\n  环带参数 (Soret 型, N=%d):\\n', N_rings);\n    fprintf('  环号  外半径[mm]  状态\\n');\n    for m = 1:N_rings\n        if mod(m,2)==1, status='开放'; else, status='遮挡'; end\n        fprintf('   %2d    %7.2f     %s\\n', m, radii_mm(m), status);\n    end\n\n    % 开放环索引 + 环带边界\n    open_rings = 1:2:N_rings;\n    r_inner = [0, radii_mm(1:end-1)] / 1000;   % [m]\n    r_outer = radii_mm / 1000;                   % [m]\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 3. 观测网格\n    % =================================================================\n    % do_quick = true  → 快速预览 ~30s, 粗网格\n    % do_quick = false → 完整精度 ~3-5min, 细网格\n    do_quick = true;\n\n    if do_quick\n        z_obs_mm = 60:10:180;    % 轴向 [mm]\n        r_obs_mm = 0:5:60;       % 径向 [mm]，只需正半轴(轴对称)\n        n_rho    = 8;            % 环带径向积分点数\n        n_theta  = 36;           % 环带角度积分点数\n    else\n        z_obs_mm = 60:4:180;\n        r_obs_mm = 0:2:60;\n        n_rho    = 16;\n        n_theta  = 72;\n    end\n\n    nz = length(z_obs_mm);\n    nr = length(r_obs_mm);\n    fprintf('\\n  网格: %d (z) x %d (r) = %d 个观测点\\n', nz, nr, nz*nr);\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 4. 声场计算 — 基尔霍夫衍射积分\n    % =================================================================\n    % 对每个观测点 (r,z):\n    %   U = Σ_{m∈开放环} ∫_{ρ_in}^{ρ_out} ∫_0^{2π} exp(ikd)/d · ρ dθ dρ\n    %   其中 d = sqrt(r² + ρ² - 2rρcosθ + z²)\n\n    fprintf('\\n  计算声场 (基尔霍夫衍射积分)...\\n');\n\n    field = zeros(nz, nr);\n    theta_vals = linspace(0, 2*pi, n_theta+1);\n    theta_vals = theta_vals(1:end-1);\n    dtheta = 2*pi / n_theta;\n\n    for iz = 1:nz\n        z_obs = z_obs_mm(iz) / 1000;  % [m]\n\n        for ir = 1:nr\n            r_obs = r_obs_mm(ir) / 1000;  % [m]\n            U = 0;  % 复声压累加器\n\n            % 轴上点 (r≈0): d = sqrt(ρ²+z²), θ积分 = 2π, 大幅加速\n            on_axis = (r_obs < 1e-9);\n\n            for m = open_rings\n                rho_vals = linspace(r_inner(m), r_outer(m), n_rho);\n                drho = (r_outer(m) - r_inner(m)) / (n_rho - 1);\n\n                for rho = rho_vals\n                    if on_axis\n                        d = sqrt(rho^2 + z_obs^2);\n                        U = U + (exp(1i*k*d)/d) * rho * drho * 2*pi;\n                    else\n                        for theta = theta_vals\n                            xs = rho * cos(theta);\n                            ys = rho * sin(theta);\n                            d = sqrt((r_obs-xs)^2 + ys^2 + z_obs^2);\n                            U = U + (exp(1i*k*d)/d) * rho * drho * dtheta;\n                        end\n                    end\n                end\n            end\n\n            field(iz, ir) = abs(U);\n        end\n\n        if mod(iz, max(1,floor(nz/10))) == 0 || iz == nz\n            fprintf('    z=%3.0fmm  (%d/%d, %.0f%%)\\n', ...\n                    z_obs_mm(iz), iz, nz, iz/nz*100);\n        end\n    end\n\n    field_dB = 20 * log10(field / max(field(:)));\n    fprintf('  计算耗时: %.1f 秒\\n', toc(t_start));\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 5. 无波带片对照（球面波 1/r 衰减）\n    % =================================================================\n    field_no = zeros(nz, nr);\n    for iz = 1:nz\n        for ir = 1:nr\n            d = sqrt((r_obs_mm(ir)/1000)^2 + (z_obs_mm(iz)/1000 + 0.300)^2);\n            field_no(iz, ir) = 1 / d;\n        end\n    end\n    field_no_dB = 20 * log10(field_no / max(field_no(:)));\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 6. 粗定位 + 增益计算\n    % =================================================================\n    [~, idx_max] = max(field(:));\n    [iz_peak, ir_peak] = ind2sub(size(field), idx_max);\n    z_coarse = z_obs_mm(iz_peak);\n    r_coarse = r_obs_mm(ir_peak);\n\n    % 焦点增益（相对于无波带片同位置）\n    gain_dB = 20 * log10(field(iz_peak, ir_peak) / ...\n                         (field_no(iz_peak, ir_peak) + eps));\n\n    fprintf('\\n  网格粗定位:\\n');\n    fprintf('    峰值位置: z=%.0f mm, r=%.0f mm\\n', z_coarse, r_coarse);\n    fprintf('    焦距偏差: %.1f mm\\n', z_coarse - 120);\n    fprintf('    焦点增益: %.1f dB\\n', gain_dB);\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 7. 亚像素二维高斯拟合\n    % =================================================================\n    fprintf('\\n  亚像素高斯拟合...\\n');\n\n    % 截取 ROI\n    roi_half = ceil(20 / (z_obs_mm(2)-z_obs_mm(1)));  % 约 ±20mm\n    roi_half = max(3, min(roi_half, 8));\n    iz1 = max(1, iz_peak - roi_half);\n    iz2 = min(nz, iz_peak + roi_half);\n    ir1 = max(1, ir_peak - roi_half);\n    ir2 = min(nr, ir_peak + roi_half);\n\n    z_roi = z_obs_mm(iz1:iz2);\n    r_roi = r_obs_mm(ir1:ir2);\n    field_roi = field(iz1:iz2, ir1:ir2);\n\n    [Rg, Zg] = meshgrid(r_roi, z_roi);\n\n    % 初值猜测\n    p0 = [max(field_roi(:))-min(field_roi(:)), ...  % A\n          r_coarse, z_coarse, ...                    % r0, z0\n          5, 15, ...                                 % σr, σz\n          min(field_roi(:))];                        % B\n\n    % 二维高斯函数\n    gauss2d = @(p,X) p(1)*exp(-((X(:,2)-p(2)).^2)/(2*p(4)^2) ...\n                              -((X(:,1)-p(3)).^2)/(2*p(5)^2)) + p(6);\n\n    X_data = [Zg(:), Rg(:)];  % 注意: X(:,1)=z, X(:,2)=r\n    Y_data = field_roi(:);\n\n    lb = [-inf, r_roi(1), z_roi(1), 0.5, 0.5, 0];\n    ub = [ inf, r_roi(end), z_roi(end), r_roi(end), z_roi(end), inf];\n\n    opts = optimoptions('lsqcurvefit', 'Display', 'off', ...\n                        'MaxFunctionEvaluations', 10000);\n\n    try\n        p_fit = lsqcurvefit(gauss2d, p0, X_data, Y_data, lb, ub, opts);\n\n        A_fit  = p_fit(1);  r0_fit = p_fit(2);\n        z0_fit = p_fit(3);  sr_fit = p_fit(4);\n        sz_fit = p_fit(5);  B_fit  = p_fit(6);\n\n        FWHM_r = 2.355 * sr_fit;\n        FWHM_z = 2.355 * sz_fit;\n\n        fprintf('    拟合结果:\\n');\n        fprintf('      r0      = %.2f mm\\n', r0_fit);\n        fprintf('      z0      = %.1f mm\\n', z0_fit);\n        fprintf('      FWHM_r  = %.1f mm\\n', FWHM_r);\n        fprintf('      FWHM_z  = %.1f mm\\n', FWHM_z);\n        fprintf('      焦距偏差 = %.1f mm (%.1f%%)\\n', ...\n                abs(z0_fit-120), abs(z0_fit-120)/120*100);\n\n        fprintf('\\n  精度对比:\\n');\n        step = z_obs_mm(2)-z_obs_mm(1);\n        fprintf('    传统(网格max):  精度 ±%.1f mm\\n', step/2);\n        fprintf('    亚像素(高斯拟合): 精度 ~%.1f mm\\n', ...\n                max(abs(r0_fit-r_coarse), abs(z0_fit-z_coarse)));\n        has_fit = true;\n    catch\n        fprintf('    拟合未收敛，使用网格值\\n');\n        r0_fit = r_coarse;  z0_fit = z_coarse;\n        FWHM_r = NaN;  FWHM_z = NaN;\n        has_fit = false;\n    end\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 8. 可视化 — 四合一图\n    % =================================================================\n    fprintf('\\n  生成图表...\\n');\n\n    figure('Position', [50, 50, 1300, 950], ...\n           'Name', '超声菲涅尔波带片声场仿真');\n\n    % --- (a) 声场热图 ---\n    subplot(2,2,1);\n    imagesc(r_obs_mm, z_obs_mm, field_dB);\n    colormap(gca, jet); colorbar;\n    set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal');\n    hold on;\n    if has_fit\n        plot(r0_fit, z0_fit, 'go', 'MarkerSize', 12, ...\n             'MarkerFaceColor', 'none', 'LineWidth', 2.5);\n    end\n    plot(r_coarse, z_coarse, 'rx', 'MarkerSize', 10, 'LineWidth', 2);\n    yline(120, 'c--', 'LineWidth', 1.2);\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('z [mm]');\n    title(sprintf('(a) 声压分布 [dB]\\n(绿圈=拟合焦点, 红叉=网格max, 虚线=F=120)'));\n    caxis([-25, 0]);\n\n    % --- (b) 轴向声压曲线 ---\n    subplot(2,2,2);\n    axial = field(:, 1);\n    plot(z_obs_mm, axial/max(axial), 'b-', 'LineWidth', 2);\n    hold on;\n    xline(z0_fit, 'g--', 'LineWidth', 1.5);\n    xline(120, 'c--', 'LineWidth', 1);\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('z [mm]'); ylabel('归一化声压');\n    title('(b) 轴向声压 U(z) | r=0');\n    legend('U(z)', sprintf('z0=%.1fmm', z0_fit), 'F=120mm', ...\n           'Location', 'best');\n    grid on;\n\n    % --- (c) 焦平面径向曲线 ---\n    subplot(2,2,3);\n    radial = field(iz_peak, :);\n    plot(r_obs_mm, radial/max(radial), 'r-', 'LineWidth', 2);\n    hold on;\n    if has_fit\n        % 标记半高点\n        half_idx = find(radial > max(radial)/2, 1, 'last');\n        if half_idx < nr\n            xline(r_obs_mm(half_idx), 'r:', 'LineWidth', 1);\n            xline(-r_obs_mm(half_idx), 'r:', 'LineWidth', 1);\n        end\n    end\n    xline(r0_fit, 'g--', 'LineWidth', 1.5);\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('归一化声压');\n    title(sprintf('(c) 焦平面径向 U(r) | z≈%.0fmm', z_coarse));\n    grid on;\n\n    % --- (d) 焦点区域等高线 ---\n    subplot(2,2,4);\n    z_zm = z_obs_mm >= z0_fit-25 & z_obs_mm <= z0_fit+25;\n    r_zm = r_obs_mm >= -25 & r_obs_mm <= 25;\n    if sum(z_zm) > 2 && sum(r_zm) > 2\n        contourf(r_obs_mm(r_zm), z_obs_mm(z_zm), field(z_zm, r_zm), 20);\n        colormap(gca, jet); colorbar;\n        set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal');\n        hold on;\n        if has_fit\n            plot(r0_fit, z0_fit, 'go', 'MarkerSize', 12, ...\n                 'MarkerFaceColor', 'none', 'LineWidth', 2.5);\n            th = linspace(0, 2*pi, 100);\n            plot(r0_fit+sr_fit*cos(th), z0_fit+sz_fit*sin(th), ...\n                 'g--', 'LineWidth', 1.5);\n        end\n        hold off;\n    end\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('z [mm]');\n    if has_fit\n        title(sprintf(['(d) 焦点等高线 + 1σ椭圆\\n' ...\n                       'FWHM_r=%.1f, FWHM_z=%.1f mm, Gain=%.1f dB'], ...\n                       FWHM_r, FWHM_z, gain_dB));\n    end\n\n    sgtitle('超声菲涅尔波带片 — MATLAB 基尔霍夫衍射积分仿真', ...\n            'FontSize', 14, 'FontWeight', 'bold');\n    saveas(gcf, 'matlab_results_main.png');\n    fprintf('    -> matlab_results_main.png\\n');\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 9. 有无波带片对比\n    % =================================================================\n    figure('Position', [100, 100, 1000, 420], 'Name', '聚焦效果对比');\n\n    subplot(1,2,1);\n    imagesc(r_obs_mm, z_obs_mm, field_dB);\n    colormap(gca, jet); colorbar;\n    set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal');\n    hold on;\n    if has_fit\n        plot(r0_fit, z0_fit, 'go', 'MarkerSize', 12, ...\n             'MarkerFaceColor', 'none', 'LineWidth', 2);\n    end\n    hold off;\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('z [mm]');\n    title(sprintf('(a) 有波带片 (N=10, F=120mm)\\n增益=%.1f dB', gain_dB));\n    caxis([-25, 0]);\n\n    subplot(1,2,2);\n    imagesc(r_obs_mm, z_obs_mm, field_no_dB);\n    colormap(gca, jet); colorbar;\n    set(gca, 'YDir', 'normal');\n    xlabel('r [mm]'); ylabel('z [mm]');\n    title('(b) 无波带片 (球面波衰减)');\n    caxis([-25, 0]);\n\n    sgtitle('菲涅尔波带片聚焦效应验证', ...\n            'FontSize', 14, 'FontWeight', 'bold');\n    saveas(gcf, 'matlab_results_comparison.png');\n    fprintf('    -> matlab_results_comparison.png\\n');\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 10. 保存数据\n    % =================================================================\n    fprintf('\\n  保存数据...\\n');\n\n    % .mat 文件（MATLAB 专用，可后续加载分析）\n    save('fresnel_data.mat', ...\n         'z_obs_mm', 'r_obs_mm', 'field', 'field_dB', ...\n         'r0_fit', 'z0_fit', 'FWHM_r', 'FWHM_z', 'gain_dB');\n\n    % CSV 文件（通用格式，Python 也能读）\n    fid = fopen('matlab_scan_data.csv', 'w');\n    fprintf(fid, 'z_mm,r_mm,pressure_norm,dB\\n');\n    for iz = 1:nz\n        for ir = 1:nr\n            fprintf(fid, '%.1f,%.1f,%.6f,%.2f\\n', ...\n                    z_obs_mm(iz), r_obs_mm(ir), ...\n                    field(iz,ir)/max(field(:)), field_dB(iz,ir));\n        end\n    end\n    fclose(fid);\n    fprintf('    -> fresnel_data.mat\\n');\n    fprintf('    -> matlab_scan_data.csv\\n');\n\n    % =================================================================\n    % 完成\n    % =================================================================\n    fprintf('\\n========================================\\n');\n    fprintf('  仿真完成！总耗时: %.1f 秒\\n', toc(t_start));\n    if has_fit\n        fprintf('  焦点: r0=%.2f mm, z0=%.1f mm\\n', r0_fit, z0_fit);\n        fprintf('  增益: %.1f dB\\n', gain_dB);\n    end\n    fprintf('========================================\\n');\nend\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":93,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":254208,"output_tokens":5127,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"a2d4108a-3635-4f31-9e1b-40e63e0e286d","timestamp":"2026-07-05T04:28:07.045Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
