{"parentUuid":"5ef14b37-245c-4519-87c0-31175b25dd23","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"a14e6667-24c5-4060-80bf-17df0e4a3e27","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-pro","content":[{"type":"text","text":"脚本已写：**`D:\\钉钉\\学习工作文件\\物理实验创新竞赛\\fresnel_sim.m`**\n\n---\n\n### 你装好 MATLAB 之后，我要做的事\n\n只需要你告诉我\"MATLAB 装好了\"，我就开始：\n\n1. **先跑快速模式**（`do_quick = true`，约 30 秒）→ 看焦点在不在 120mm 附近\n2. 确认方向对了 →**切完整模式**（`do_quick = false`，约 3-5 分钟）→ 出正式结果\n3. 调参数（改网格密度、环数 N、噪声水平）→ 跑变参对比\n4. 自动输出：\n   - `matlab_results_main.png` → 四合一图（热图+轴向+径向+焦点放大）\n   - `matlab_results_comparison.png` → 有无波带片对比\n   - `matlab_scan_data.csv` → 数据表，可以直接喂给 Python 脚本做高斯拟合\n   - `fresnel_data.mat` → MATLAB 数据文件，后续可加载继续分析\n\n全程你不需要碰 MATLAB 界面。我就跟操作 Python 一样操作它。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5413,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":254208,"output_tokens":296,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"stop_details":null},"type":"assistant","uuid":"2993d305-70c8-4cd7-bc82-accf0f370242","timestamp":"2026-07-05T06:20:45.744Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"d:\\豆包\\vscode文件","sessionId":"2563aa1c-2760-4099-ae80-555560773076","version":"2.1.145","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"claude-code-comsol-comsol-multiphysics-groovy-otter"}
